With this endpoint you can post a vote for a given domain. The body for the POST request must be the JSON representation of a [vote object](https://gtidocs.virustotal.com/reference/vote-object). Note however that you don't need to provide an ID for the object, as they are automatically generated for new votes.

The verdict attribute must have be either harmless or malicious.

```json Example request
{
  "data": {
    "type": "vote",
    "attributes": {
    	"verdict": "harmless"
    }
  }
}
```

